  stats
    stat at 30,5 element Object p1 cp437:0x47 under Normal color 0x66
    oop
    @gate
    :touch
    The bakery gate. Warm and shut.
    #if haskey open
    A brass keyhole waits, empty.
    The bread waits harder.
    #end
    :open
    Your key turns with a buttery click.
    #play tcf
    #put north empty
    #die
    :hint
    #end
    end
    stat at 20,20 element Object p1 cp437:0x42 under Empty color 0x07
    oop
    @baker
    :touch
    Apron dusted, thumbs tapping.
    "Locked myself out again.
    Dropped the gate key in the
    fountain, of all the wet luck."
    !east;Head east to the fountain?
    #end
    :east
    "Roll up your sleeves."
    #go east
    #end
    end
    stat at 40,20 element Object p1 cp437:0x50 under Empty color 0x07
    oop
    @patron
    :touch
    A regular, nursing a cold roll.
    "Benches west, gossip's better
    there. Fountain's east if you
    fancy wet feet."
    #end
    end
  end
end

