  stats
    stat at 30,12 element Object cycle 3 p1 cp437:0x2A under Normal color 0x99
    oop
    @key
    :touch
    Half-sunk in the fountain: the bakery key.
    Your socks are already ruined. Grab it.
    #give key
    #play tcfg
    Got it. The gate will forgive you now.
    #die
    #end
    end
    stat at 12,8 element Object cycle 3 p1 cp437:0x6F under Water color 0x9F
    oop
    @spout
    :touch
    The west spout sputters and apologizes.
    It has been under-maintained since the bakery locked up.
    #end
    end
  end
end

