    @gatebar
    :touch
    The iron bar of the bakery gate.
    A yellow keyhole waits, smug.
    #if key yellow open
    Still locked. You have no yellow key.
    #end
    :open
    #end
    end
    stat at 47,12 element Object p1 cp437:0x4F under Empty color 0x07
    oop
    @bell
    :touch
    A service bell, tarnished, hopeful.
    You ring it.
    #play tcd
    Nobody answers. The gate stays shut.
    Maybe the fountain in the plaza is
    hiding what you need.
    #end
    end
