    @baker
    :touch
    You made it past the gate!
    Welcome, welcome. Sit anywhere.
    $The Warm Bread Plaza, now open.
    Would you like something?
    !bread;A warm loaf, please
    !nothing;Just admiring the place
    #end
    :bread
    The baker beams and hands you
    a loaf the size of a small dog.
    #play tcef
